    skos:definition "Forests dominated by Pinus sylvestris and Pinus nigra in temperate continental, Temperate and submediterranean montane and Mediterranean montane conditions, and Pinus heldreichii-Pinus peuce forest in Mediterranean and Balkan subalpine conditions. Includes burnt areas of this type."@en ;
    skos:broader <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/ecosystems/typologies/4.2> ;
