    skos:scopeNote "Including stands of non-native trees species that have long been established in European forest mixes."@en ;
    skos:definition "Mixed plantations of broadleaved evergreen species where at least one constituent is exotic or outside its natural range, or if composed of native species then managed intensively and planted in mono-age stands. Mono-cultural plantations of recently introduced species should be assigned to 4.6.1. Includes burnt areas of this type."@en ;
